# Summary
This documentation explains Amplitude's Data Access Control (DAC) feature for Enterprise customers, which allows administrators to restrict access to sensitive data (PII, revenue, sensitive information) by classifying properties and setting group-level permissions, with enforcement across charts, cohorts, dashboards, exports, and APIs.

